title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options' and not 'www.actuate.com'
OB: When the user clicks on 'OK' and then reopens the hyperlink builder, the title of the builder changes to 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected behavior is that the title of the hyperlink builder should remain as 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Click on 'OK' to close the hyperlink builder.
2. Reopen the hyperlink builder and observe the title change to 'www.actuate.com'.
